    <item>
      <title>奥尔班通过向民族主义者提供银行贷款建立极右翼影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/hungary-s-orban-builds-far-right-influence-with-bank-loans-to-nationalists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙之声党成为最新一个从匈牙利银行获得贷款以资助政治运动的极右翼团体，这是总理维克托·奥尔班在欧洲同胞民族主义者中建立影响力的方式之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/hungary-s-orban-builds-far-right-influence-with-bank-loans-to-nationalists</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:30:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国将实现欧盟 3% 赤字上限的计划推迟至 2029 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/france-delays-plan-to-meet-3-eu-deficit-limit-until-2029</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 将把预算赤字控制在欧盟限额内的目标推迟了两年，以便为修复国家公共财政赢得喘息空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/france-delays-plan-to-meet-3-eu-deficit-limit-until-2029</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:18:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰推出企业税优惠预算案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/ireland-delivers-giveaway-budget-on-corporation-tax-boon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰政府已提交了一份丰厚的 2025 年预算，向选民赠送了几份礼物，这要归功于预计将创纪录的公司税收和苹果公司的补缴税款将带来的充裕国库。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/ireland-delivers-giveaway-budget-on-corporation-tax-boon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:11:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯军队围困数月后进入乌克兰前哨基地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/russian-forces-enter-embattled-outpost-vuhledar-after-months-of-siege</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫军队在乌克兰东部前线发起进攻，而基辅当局则竭力阻止，俄罗斯军队随即进入乌克兰东部前线的一个前哨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/russian-forces-enter-embattled-outpost-vuhledar-after-months-of-siege</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:58:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>突尼斯总统竞选者因选举临近被判入狱多年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/tunisian-presidential-challenger-jailed-for-years-as-vote-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在突尼斯总统凯斯·赛义德即将举行大选的五天前，该北非国家现任总统有望轻松获胜的两名选举竞争对手之一因涉嫌伪造文件而再次被判入狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/tunisian-presidential-challenger-jailed-for-years-as-vote-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:43:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨顾问称，投票前征收电动汽车关税不是“好主意”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/scholz-adviser-says-ev-tariffs-not-good-idea-ahead-of-eu-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国仍然对欧盟对中国制造的进口电动汽车征收关税持怀疑态度，并仍希望在周五成员国投票前通过谈判找到解决方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/scholz-adviser-says-ev-tariffs-not-good-idea-ahead-of-eu-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:06:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国逮捕一名中国女子，涉嫌窃取武器供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/germany-arrests-chinese-woman-for-spying-on-weapon-supplies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国检察官逮捕了一名被指控监视通过莱比锡机场运输武器物资的中国公民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/germany-arrests-chinese-woman-for-spying-on-weapon-supplies</guid>
